{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, because the update matrices can be removed, LoRA can be combined with any other adapters (Poth et al., 2023).",
    "Methods DataThe Automated Student Assessment Prize (ASAP) AES and SAS datasets were originally made available to the public via two competitions hosted by Kaggle in 2012 (Shermis, 2014(Shermis, 2015)).",
    "The AES dataset encompasses a total of 12,978 essays, spanning 8 distinct stimuli.",
    "3 The SAS dataset consists of 17,043 total responses across 10 items that span various subjects, administered to students in grades 8 and 10 (depending on the item).",
    "Each response was scored by two human annotators."
  ]
}